r> </mrow> </math><br /><br />Number of B atoms at octahedral voids = Number of O-atoms = 4<br /><br />Number of A atoms at tetrahedral voids<br /><br />= 2 x Number of O-atoms<br /><br />= 2 x 4 = 8<br /><br />Initial formula of compound is A<sub>8 </sub>B<sub>4</sub> O<sub>4</sub><br /><br />After removal about two body diagonal<br /><br />A atom <math> <mrow> <mo>&rArr;</mo> <mn>8</mn> <mo>-</mo> <mn>4</mn> <mo>=</mo> <mn>4</mn> </mrow> </math>&nbsp;&nbsp; (Removed from 2 body diagonals)<br /><br />B atoms <math> <mrow> <mo>&rArr;</mo> <mn>4</mn> <mo>-</mo> <mn>1</mn> <mo>=</mo> <mn>3</mn> </mrow> </math> &nbsp;&nbsp; (Removed from body centre)<br /><br />O atom <math> <mrow> <mo>&rArr;</mo> <mn>4</mn> <mo>-</mo> <mn>4</mn> <mo>&times;</mo> <mfrac> <mrow> <mn>1</mn> </mrow> <mrow> <mn>8</mn> </mrow> </mfrac> <mo>=</mo> <mn>3.5</mn> </mrow> </math> &nbsp;&nbsp; (Removed 4 corners)<br /><br />Formula will be A<sub>4</sub>B<sub>3</sub>O<sub>3.5</sub> i.e. A<sub>8</sub>B<sub>6</sub>O<sub>7</sub>", "image": null}, "videoSolution": null, "numericalLowerLimit": null, "numericalUpperLimit": null, "cpyqbSubjects": ["615f0cf69476412f48314dac", "616057040283de43c87e3e16", "61bb58281213731910ea0b71", "6160579d0283de43c87e3e1f", "61964f94a5a526011886801e", "61c055f6e8ce0dc8a5c62d34", "61a8a2cce8ce0dc8a5c62d2e", "6160577e0283de43c87e3e1c", "616057210283de43c87e3e19", "629105adee9e3ae00d63352c", "62962075e7f8e9ac4daeafd8", "629f385f263330a77be9fa7e", "629f39e4ac11b26562e0625c", "61964ff3a5a5260118868022", "64d50c263df7f4a7f3017f70", "66b79b89d4b564dfab4f94d0", "678ea9a09cc79e5f592bdc12", "67fa602f4468eb1307ceb0ae", "6807d350647479b8e869647a"], "cpyqbChapters": ["616024c47628a8df01cb48c7", "616024c5212b28f0d9886af8", "61964ca6146849521d9afe86", "61c089bc175602fa2089f997", "61e7bd81485abb823f4d4e5f", "61bb822dbcf0a7a48f4c9575", "616024c739e0b916d79b6bf6", "616024c50e12f91df5ea7f3f", "616024c6750aab4db7d1dfeb", "61964ca6baadf821644395b4", "629109e0d178b5b9ecf4c073", "6296211ac83d9